    "title": "Agano la Mungu na Daudi",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "agano la mungu na daudi",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Mungu alifanya makubaliano matano maalum (yanayoitwa maagano) na watu wake katika Agano la Kale:</p><ol><li><p>Mungu alimwahidi Noa, familia yake, na viumbe wote kwamba Gharika haitaharibu tena dunia (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:18\">Mwanzo 6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:1-Gen9:17\">9:1–17</a>). Hii inajulikana kama Agano la Noa.</p></li><li><p>Mungu alimuahidi Abrahamu nchi ya Kanaani na kwamba angekuwa taifa kubwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:1-Gen15:21\">Mwanzo 15:1–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:1-Gen17:27\">17:1–27</a>). Hii inajulikana kama agano la Abrahamu.</p></li><li><p>Mungu alianzisha uhusiano maalum na Israeli kwenye Mlima Sinai kupitia Mose (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:1-Exod23:33\">Kutoka 19–23</a>). Hii inaitwa Agano la Mose.</p></li><li><p>Mungu alimuahidi mwana wa Aroni, Finehasi, kwamba wazao wake watakuwa makuhani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:10-Num25:13\">Hesabu 25:10–13</a>). Hii inaitwa Agano la Kikuhani.</p></li><li><p>Mungu alimuahidi Daudi kwamba yeye na wazao wake watakuwa wafalme (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:4-2Sam7:17\">2 Samweli 7:4–17</a>). Hii inajulikana kama Agano la Daudi.</p></li></ol><p>Mungu pia aliahidi kupitia Yeremia kufanya &quot;agano jipya&quot; katika siku zijazo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:31-Jer31:34\">Yeremia 31:31–34</a>).</p><p>Kwenye <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:1-2Sam7:29\">2 Samweli 7</a>, ahadi ya Mungu kwa Daudi haijaitwa agano. Hata hivyo, vifungu vingine vinaieleza kama agano (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:5\">23:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:18\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 7:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:7\">21:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:3-Ps89:4\">Zaburi 89:3–4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:28-Ps89:29\">28–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:11-Ps132:12\">132:11–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:3\">Isaiah 55:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:20-Jer33:21\">Yeremia 33:20–21</a>). Ahadi ya Mungu kwa Daudi kwamba &quot;upendo wa kujitolea hautaondolewa&quot; inapendekeza uhusiano wa agano (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:15\">2 Samweli 7:15</a>). Kama ilivyo kwa ahadi ya Mungu kwa Abrahamu, agano lake na Daudi halina masharti. Hatimaye, inategemea upendo wa Mungu usiobadilika, siyo utiifu au uaminifu wa kibinadamu.</p><p>Sehemu muhimu zaidi ya agano la Mungu na Daudi ni ahadi ya Mungu ya kuendeleza kizazi cha Daudi na kuwa kama Baba kwao (linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:36\">1 Wafalme 11:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:4\">15:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:19\">2 Wafalme 8:19</a>). Baraka ya Mungu kwa mwana wa Daudi, Solomoni, inatimiza sehemu ya ahadi hii (linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:10-2Sam7:11\">2 Samweli 7:10–11</a> na <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:56\">1 Wafalme 8:56</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:20\">1 Wafalme 8:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:24\">24</a>). Mungu alikuwa mvumilivu kwa wafalme wa Yuda, hata walipofanya mambo mabaya. Hii ilikuwa kwa sababu ya ahadi yake kwa Daudi (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:12-1Kgs11:13\">1 Wafalme 11:12–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:3-1Kgs15:5\">15:3–5</a>).</p><p>Utimilifu kamili wa ahadi ya Mungu kwa Daudi unapatikana katika Masihi, Yesu Kristo, &quot;Mwana wa Daudi&quot; (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:27\">Mathayo 9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:30-Matt20:31\">20:30–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:9\">21:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:15\">15</a>). Isaya alitabiri kwamba mtu ambaye angetawala kutoka kiti cha enzi cha Daudi na juu ya ufalme wake …milele&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:7\">Isaya 9:7</a>). Alimwita &quot;chipukizi&quot; linalokua &quot;kutoka kwenye shina la Yese&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:1\">Isaya 11:1</a>). Marejeleo haya yanaelekeza kwa Masihi ajaye (mteule wa Mungu).</p><p>Sehemu nne katika Agano Jipya zinaonyesha kwamba Yesu anatimiza ahadi zilizotolewa kwa Daudi kwa kurejelea moja kwa moja <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:1-2Sam7:29\">2 Samweli 7:1–29</a> (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:32-Luke1:33\">Luka 1:32–33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:29-Acts2:31\">Matendo 2:29–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:22-Acts13:23\">13:22–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:5\">Waebrania 1:5</a>). Agano Jipya linaanza na kumalizika kwa kumwita Yesu &quot;mwana wa Daudi,&quot; mrithi wa kiti chake cha enzi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:1\">Mathayo 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:16\">Ufunuo 22:16</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:5-2Sam7:16\">2 Samweli 7:5–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:20-1Kgs8:24\">1 Wafalme 8:20–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:9-1Kgs11:13\">11:9–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:1-1Kgs15:5\">15:1–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:18-2Kgs8:19\">2 Wafalme 8:18–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:17-2Chr7:22\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 7:17–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:3-Ps89:4\">Zaburi 89:3–4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:18-Ps89:51\">18–51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:10-Ps132:12\">132:10–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6-Isa9:7\">Isaya 9:6–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:1-Isa11:10\">11:1–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:20-Jer33:26\">Yeremia 33:20–26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:1\">Mathayo 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:30-Matt20:31\">20:30–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:1-Matt21:9\">21:1–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:30-Luke1:33\">Luka 1:30–33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:67-Luke1:79\">67–79</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:22-Acts2:36\">Matendo 2:22–36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:16\">Ufunuo 22:16</a></p>",
